1
00:00:00,480 --> 00:00:03,880
[A midwinter day when the cold is forgotten]

2
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:07,260
[Which couple is on a drive date?]

3
00:00:07,300 --> 00:00:12,380
[Kim Sun Wook: The weather is nice.]
[Kim Su Min: It's 8 degrees today.]

4
00:00:12,380 --> 00:00:15,820
[Kim Sun Wook: That's high.]
[Kim Su Min: It's said to be about 6 degrees.]

5
00:00:15,820 --> 00:00:18,180
[Kim Sun Wook: The weather is nice.]

6
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:22,480
[Kim Su Min: I finally had my first date
on the fifth day.]

7
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:24,880
[Kim Su Min: My first date was with Sun Wook,]

8
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:27,620
[Kim Su Min: so I was full of excitement.]

9
00:00:27,880 --> 00:00:30,920
[Kim Su Min: I was nervous
even before heading out.]

10
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:33,780
[Kim Sun Wook: I didn't hesitate at all.]

11
00:00:33,780 --> 00:00:37,660
[Kim Sun Wook: I chose
Su Min and Hyun Jun right away.]

12
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,220
[Kim Su Min: Looks like a dog resort.
It says "Pet Dog Spa Pool Villa."]

13
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:44,940
[Kim Sun Wook: Spa?
There are a lot of shops.]

14
00:00:44,940 --> 00:00:48,500
[Kim Su Min: I should bring my dog here.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I know.]

15
00:00:48,980 --> 00:00:51,380
[Kim Su Min: You said you have a dog, right?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

16
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:53,420
[Kim Sun Wook: But my dog is old.]

17
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:56,500
[Kim Su Min: How old is it?]
[Kim Sun Wook: About...]

18
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:58,540
[Kim Sun Wook:
How old is it? I can't remember.]

19
00:00:58,540 --> 00:00:59,580
[Kim Sun Wook: 15 years old.]

20
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:06,900
[Kim Su Min: 15 years old is old. What breed?]
[Kim Sun Wook: A mixed-breed Yorkshire terrier.]

21
00:01:07,620 --> 00:01:09,420
[Kim Sun Wook: It's really cute.]

22
00:01:10,020 --> 00:01:12,580
[There's a dog!]
[A neighborhood dog]

23
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:14,860
[Kim Su Min: Two dogs.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah, they must live here.]

24
00:01:14,860 --> 00:01:17,700
[Kim Su Min: So cute.]
[Kim Sun Wook: How'd they come up from below?]

25
00:01:17,700 --> 00:01:19,620
[Kim Su Min: They look so gentle.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

26
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:21,580
[Kim Su Min: They have collars on.]

27
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:26,900
[Kim Su Min: My dog loves whining.]

28
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:28,660
[Kim Sun Wook: Whining?]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

29
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:30,980
[Kim Sun Wook: Mine, too.]

30
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,180
[Kim Su Min: Then it makes demands.]

31
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:37,080
[Kim Su Min: It taps you
with its front paws like this.]

32
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:39,979
[Kim Sun Wook:
Oh, it taps you. How old is it?]

33
00:01:39,979 --> 00:01:44,460
[Kim Su Min: 5 years old.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Still a baby. I like that breed.]

34
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:47,380
[Kim Sun Wook: The breed that you raise.]
[Kim Su Min: The greyhound.]

35
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:49,140
[Kim Sun Wook: Baldies are so cute.]

36
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:51,180
[Kim Su Min: Baldies.]

37
00:01:53,539 --> 00:01:55,780
[Kim Su Min: Yeah, my baldy is cute.]

38
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:58,060
[Kim Su Min: I like hairless puppies.]

39
00:01:58,060 --> 00:02:02,420
[Kim Sun Wook: Me too.
So I shave my dog every summer.]

40
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:07,340
[Really steep slope]

41
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:09,960
[Kim Su Min: Are we going
to the top of the mountain?]

42
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:12,580
[Kim Sun Wook: Right?
Is it a ride on the mountain?]

43
00:02:12,580 --> 00:02:17,540
[Kim Su Min: Is there anything here?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Right?]

44
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:22,060
[Kim Su Min: Since there are posters
on the poles, there must be something.]

45
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:32,180
[Kim Sun Wook: Somethi... Bungee jumping?]
[Kim Su Min: Huh?]

46
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:35,700
[Kim Sun Wook: Isn't it that one above?]

47
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:39,620
[Kim Su Min: Can you do it?]

48
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:40,800
[Kim Su Min: Huh?]

49
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:43,220
[Kim Sun Wook: I didn't expect
bungee jumping at all.]

50
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,940
[A thrilling date activity,
the highest in Korea]

51
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:52,860
[Electrifying bonding experience
just for the two of them]

52
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,060
We...

53
00:02:55,060 --> 00:02:57,700
[Kim Sun Wook:
I never thought about trying it.]

54
00:02:58,140 --> 00:03:01,540
[Kim Sun Wook:
This isn't it. Bungee jumping?]

55
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:06,060
[Kim Sun Wook: I just heard
that we were going on a ride.]

56
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:08,000
[Kim Sun Wook: So I thought
it was a theme park ride,]

57
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,940
[Kim Sun Wook:
like the Ferris wheel or the carousel.]

58
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:12,740
[Kim Sun Wook: But when we arrived,
we saw it was falling from somewhere high.]

59
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:17,820
[45-meter Big Swing, highest in Korea]
[Kim Sun Wook: It's another first for me here.]

60
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:22,780
[Kim Su Min: I'm uneasy even just
going down stairs without handrails.]

61
00:03:22,780 --> 00:03:27,100
[Kim Su Min: It's one of the biggest
challenges I've ever done in my life.]

62
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:31,990
[Kim Su Min: I'm so nervous right now.]
[Kim Sun Wook: It's OK. Don't be nervous.]

63
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,460
[Kim Sun Wook: No reason to be.]

64
00:03:41,579 --> 00:03:42,900
I'll stand on the left.

65
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:47,300
[Kim Su Min: Look forward.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hoo...]

66
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:52,100
[Kim Sun Wook: Hyung! Why'd you bring me here?]
[Kim Su Min: Will we be OK?]

67
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:55,260
[Kim Sun Wook: Wait.]

68
00:03:58,060 --> 00:04:02,780
[Kim Su Min: I'm actually afraid of heights.]
[Kim Sun Wook: So why'd you bring me here?]

69
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,300
[Kim Sun Wook: Why here?]

70
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:07,420
[Kim Su Min: Oh, we're going up.]

71
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:11,700
[Kim Sun Wook: Why'd you bring me here?]
[Kim Su Min: I'm sorry. I was wrong.]

72
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,300
[Kim Sun Wook: Nah. It'll be fun.]

73
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,260
[Kim Sun Wook: It must be fun.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

74
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:19,300
[Kim Sun Wook: When we were raised,
we actually went really high.]

75
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,779
[Kim Sun Wook: I heard a tip somewhere]

76
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:24,180
[Kim Sun Wook:
that when you're at a high place,]

77
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:26,740
[Kim Sun Wook:
looking far away will calm your nerves.]

78
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:29,180
[Kim Sun Wook: As I looked at
the far mountains, I was no longer scared.]

79
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:32,300
[Kim Sun Wook: So I thought
that was the moment I should do it.]

80
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:33,380
[Kim Sun Wook: But when
I pulled on the red rope...]

81
00:04:33,380 --> 00:04:34,460
[Let's go!]

82
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:38,980
[Kim Sun Wook: Wait, I can't pull the rope.
I'm so scared.]

83
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,380
[Ah!]

84
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:54,740
[Leaning on each other
as they feel the thrill]

85
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:01,900
[Kim Su Min: I screamed
like I'd never screamed before.]

86
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:06,980
[Kim Sun Wook: But it's beautiful.]

87
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:10,940
[Taking in the vast scenery in one go]

88
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:22,980
[Kim Sun Wook: It was fun. I want to do it again.]
[Kim Su Min: I can do it once more.]

89
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:28,740
[We did it! We did it.]

90
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,180
We did it.

91
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:31,800
[Kim Sun Wook: Now I'm calm enough
to enjoy the scenery.]

92
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,860
[Kim Su Min: I'm tearing up.]

93
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:36,420
[Finally able to enjoy the vast scenery]

94
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:40,180
[Kim Su Min: I screamed really loud, didnt I?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Me too.]

95
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:43,260
[Kim Su Min: I did it.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Good job.]

96
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:47,460
[Kim Su Min: Is my hair OK?]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, wait.]

97
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:52,540
[Kim Su Min:
Both of our hair became messy.]

98
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:57,900
[Kim Su Min: We fixed each other's hair,
and exchanged those subtle touches.]

99
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,460
[Kim Su Min: I had fun.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah?]

100
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:02,340
[Kim Su Min: Yeah, it was quite fun.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I had fun too.]

101
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:10,180
[Gureumsan Cafe]
[A cup of coffee to unwind
after the extreme thrill]

102
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:16,260
[Coughing]

103
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:24,300
[Kim Su Min: Oh no, you keep coughing.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I know.]

104
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,420
Thank you.

105
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,060
[Kim Su Min: You can have both.]

106
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:32,220
[Kim Su Min: They're already warm.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Thank you.]

107
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:37,220
[Kim Sun Wook: But it was really fun.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah? That's good.]

108
00:06:37,220 --> 00:06:43,060
[Kim Su Min: I screamed so much just now.]
[Kim Sun Wook: That's normal. It was scary.]

109
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:46,980
[Kim Su Min: It was scary.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I screamed too.]

110
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:50,020
[Kim Su Min: I couldn't hear anything else.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

111
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:51,900
[Kim Su Min: It was just my fear and me.]

112
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:56,180
[Kim Sun Wook: I think I heard other stuff.]
[Kim Su Min: My voice was really loud.]

113
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:59,580
[Kim Sun Wook:
I don't think I was any softer.]

114
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:04,540
[Kim Su Min: It was OK after the fall,
when it was just swaying.]

115
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:14,860
[Kim Sun Wook: It's still nice to be outside.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

116
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:17,100
[Kim Sun Wook: You asked me out on a date.]

117
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:18,460
[Kim Sun Wook: I kept my promise.]

118
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:24,660
[Kim Su Min: I'm so happy to be on this date.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Me too.]

119
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:28,060
[Kim Sun Wook:
I wanted to go on one date with you.]

120
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:31,100
[Kim Su Min: Do you know this?
You're my first date in this shoot.]

121
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:29,260
What?

122
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:34,100
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

123
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:35,300
My first date.

124
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:37,540
[His first date with Sun Wook
after a long wait]

125
00:07:37,820 --> 00:07:39,980
[Kim Su Min: I'm so happy.]

126
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:42,580
[Kim Sun Wook: That's good.]

127
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:46,020
[Kim Sun Wook: Actually, I'm curious.]

128
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:48,540
[Kim Sun Wook: There are many new faces.]

129
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:51,620
[Kim Sun Wook: Is there
anyone you want to get to know?]

130
00:07:53,460 --> 00:08:00,820
[Kim Su Min: Um... There was.
I wasn't totally uninterested.]

131
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:05,580
[Kim Su Min: There was
someone I was curious about.]

132
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:10,500
[Kim Su Min: We had brief conversations.]

133
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:18,100
[Kim Su Min:
But my heart has never changed.]

134
00:08:19,380 --> 00:08:22,180
[Kim Sun Wook: Am I...
worthy of such devotion?]

135
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:27,180
[I guess I really like you.]

136
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:36,100
[Kim Sun Wook: Actually I...
can't hide my feelings, right?]

137
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:42,500
[Kim Sun Wook: After receiving your call
yesterday too, I was really surprised.]

138
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:46,900
[Kim Sun Wook: I was surprised,
but I really felt the sincerity in your words,]

139
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:51,220
[Kim Sun Wook: about how you were thankful.]

140
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:54,820
[I'm really thankful to you too.]

141
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:59,580
[Kim Su Min:
Before we went bowling yesterday,]

142
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:04,540
[Kim Su Min: I had a lot on my mind
and was very confused.]

143
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:09,860
[Kim Su Min: But when I saw you
having fun bowling and being happy,]

144
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:14,980
[Kim Su Min: I felt a lot better.]

145
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:17,540
[Kim Su Min: Like your presence alone
warms my heart?]

146
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,420
[Kim Sun Wook: Sorry?]

147
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:24,900
[Kim Sun Wook: What should I do?]

148
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:31,380
[Kim Su Min: So whatever it is,
I just hope that you can be happy.]

149
00:09:35,180 --> 00:09:38,260
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm happy right now.]

150
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:45,780
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm grateful for what he said.
It warmed my heart.]

151
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:50,300
[Kim Sun Wook: I think
wishing someone happiness is really profound.]

152
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:53,540
[Kim Sun Wook: It means you hope
everything goes smoothly for them,]

153
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:55,300
[Kim Sun Wook: and you hope their days]

154
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:58,380
[Kim Sun Wook:
are filled with peace and happiness.]

155
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:00,380
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm very grateful,]

156
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:02,420
[Kim Sun Wook: but also...]

157
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:09,940
[Kim Sun Wook: I was at a loss.
Compared to what he does for me,]

158
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:12,100
[Kim Sun Wook:
there's nothing I can do for him.]

159
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:16,060
[Kim Sun Wook: The time I spent with you
is also precious to me.]

160
00:10:17,060 --> 00:10:18,780
[Kim Su Min: I'm happy to hear that.]

161
00:10:19,140 --> 00:10:24,540
[Kim Sun Wook: That's why I chose you.]
[Kim Su Min: I see.]

162
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:27,980
[Kim Su Min: For the past five days,
I've felt too many emotions.]

163
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:30,140
[Kim Sun Wook: Why? Why?]

164
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,980
[Kim Su Min: Just in my heart.]

165
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:35,620
[Kim Su Min: I feel confused,
then organize my thoughts,]

166
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:39,260
[Kim Su Min: then get stressed out,
and don't know what to do...]

167
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:42,220
[Kim Su Min:
Just constant mood fluctuations.]

168
00:10:42,220 --> 00:10:46,500
[Kim Su Min: But after yesterday,
I've found peace of mind.]

169
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:49,780
[Kim Su Min: After yesterday.]

170
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:53,140
[Kim Su Min: Because I've
fully processed my feelings.]

171
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:57,660
[Kim Su Min: It'd be great
if our happinesses were aligned,]

172
00:10:57,660 --> 00:11:00,540
[Kim Su Min: but after hearing
Sun Wook convey his gratitude]

173
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:06,100
[Kim Su Min: and also knowing
where Sun Wook's heart lies...]

174
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:12,540
[I'll wish him well from afar...]

175
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:20,420
[Kim Sun Wook: I brought this.]

176
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:25,700
[Kim Sun Wook:
We have to take photos with this.]

177
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:29,140
[Kim Su Min: OK. Sure.]

178
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:32,700
[Kim Su Min: Have you been taking photos?]
[Kim Sun Wook: A bit? I've taken...]

179
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:36,620
[Kim Sun Wook: about a dozen?]
[Kim Su Min: That's a lot.]

180
00:11:37,020 --> 00:11:38,620
[Kim Su Min: Use it up in this stay.]

181
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,420
Does it work like this?

182
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:46,940
[They record today's memories
with the film camera]

183
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:50,740
-Think you've got it. -Yeah?

184
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:05,060
[Kim Sun Wook: So handsome.]

185
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:07,020
[Kim Su Min: That date itself]

186
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:11,540
[Kim Su Min: with Sun Wook
gave me butterflies. I really enjoyed it.]

187
00:12:11,540 --> 00:12:14,540
[Kim Su Min:
Seeing the person I like happy]

188
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:17,460
[Kim Su Min: really brings me happiness.]

189
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:20,500
[Kim Sun Wook:
Through my conversations with Su Min,]

190
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:23,420
[Kim Sun Wook: I really felt appreciated,
realizing that I'm actually]

191
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:25,300
[Kim Sun Wook:
a good person in someone's eyes.]

192
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:27,860
[Kim Sun Wook:
It was really comforting, because]

193
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:30,500
[Kim Sun Wook:
I'm usually very critical of myself.]

194
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:32,180
[Kim Sun Wook:
Of course I have my strengths too.]

195
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:35,420
[Kim Sun Wook:
When I talk about my flaws,]

196
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:37,500
[Kim Sun Wook:
there weren't many people who]

197
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:39,180
[Kim Sun Wook:
told me that they aren't flaws.]

198
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,780
[Kim Sun Wook: But Su Min is different.]

199
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:46,620
[Kim Sun Wook: With this,
I'm really grateful and touched.]

200
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:49,140
[Kim Sun Wook: I had a lot of fun today.]
[Kim Su Min: Me too.]

201
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:53,020
[Kim Sun Wook: I didn't imagine
you to bring me on a sky-drop date.]

202
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:55,820
[Kim Sun Wook: I'll never forget it.]

203
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:58,860
[Kim Su Min:
I think I'll think about it often too.]

204
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:01,940
-Every time I look at high places. -Yeah.

205
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:03,220
[A day that will be
etched in their memories]

206
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:05,700
[While those who got a match
went on their dates,]

207
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:08,340
[what's going on with those
who remained in Men's House?]

208
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:11,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I got all dressed up
only to stay at home.]

209
00:13:18,580 --> 00:13:20,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
What should we have for lunch?]

210
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:22,900
[Oh Min Seong: What do you want to eat?
I'll cook for you.]

211
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:25,700
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

212
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,590
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I wanted to cook for you.]

213
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,420
[Oh Min Seong: I don't believe you.]

214
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:35,140
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I want Korean food.]
