[Lee Hyeong Jun: I can't stand it
when things feel awkward.]

419
00:28:17,060 --> 00:28:18,820
[Oh Min Seong:
Doesn't that apply to everyone?]

420
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:21,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Here we go again.]

421
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:25,980
[Oh Min Seong: Who likes being awkward?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Even when I'm praising you...]

422
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:28,420
[Oh Min Seong:
I did some reflection yesterday.]

423
00:28:28,420 --> 00:28:31,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Reflection?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

424
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:32,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why?]

425
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:35,660
[Oh Min Seong: Yesterday,
I suddenly thought of the fact that]

426
00:28:35,660 --> 00:28:40,260
