more considerate of your stance.]

427
00:28:44,020 --> 00:28:47,260
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Don't worry about it.]

428
00:28:47,260 --> 00:28:50,980
[Oh Min Seong: I felt it yesterday.]

429
00:28:52,420 --> 00:29:03,980
[Oh Min Seong: Anyway, when I
thought about it, I did what I did for myself.]

430
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:06,940
[Oh Min Seong: But that could be
a lot of pressure on you.]

431
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:16,460
[Oh Min Seong: So I thought
that I was anxious and being impatient.]

432
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:18,260
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah. I'd jumped the gun.]

433
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:25,180
[Oh Min Seong: That's what I thought.]

434
00:29:29,180 --> 00:29:36,580
[Oh Min Seong: So I understand everything.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: OK.]

435
00:29:36,580 --> 00:29:39,340
[Oh Min Seong:
Yes, I understand everything.]

436
00:29:40,380 --> 00:29:43,420
[Oh Min Seong:
After our dates every day, I still like him.]

437
00:29:43,420 --> 00:29:48,580
[Oh Min Seong: My interest didn't decrease
