443
00:30:11,740 --> 00:30:13,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: so I didn't hate it.]

444
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:17,460
[Oh Min Seong: Did you like it?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Not really.]

445
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Just like that.]

446
00:30:20,100 --> 00:30:23,660
[Oh Min Seong: Sigh.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What?]

447
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:25,220
[Oh Min Seong: Just don't talk.]

448
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:28,180
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Should I?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yes, stop talking.]

449
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:31,240
[Oh Min Seong:
I just hope you don't feel pressured.]

450
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,300
[Lee Hyeong Jun: OK.]

451
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:38,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
The more I date him, the more I like him.]

452
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:42,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I saw more and more
