Eum Hyeok Jin: Oh, well.]

540
00:36:07,700 --> 00:36:08,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: Thank you.]

541
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:18,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You can smell the floral scent
