542
00:36:19,540 --> 00:36:22,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: This is nice.
The fragrance is pleasant.]

543
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:24,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right?
Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

544
00:36:24,460 --> 00:36:26,140
