576
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:43,460
[Kim Han Gyeol: for the rest of the time.]

577
00:38:45,220 --> 00:38:47,540
[Kim Su Min: You seem to have
a lot of thoughts.]

578
00:38:47,540 --> 00:38:49,420
[Kim Han Gyeol: I do think a lot.]

579
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:51,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: But given my personality,]

580
00:38:51,740 --> 00:38:54,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm not really the type
to share my thoughts with others.]

581
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:56,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: I've always found it difficult.]

582
00:38:56,820 --> 00:39:00,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: From the beginning
until this moment,]

583
00:39:00,060 --> 00:39:01,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: there hasn't been
a single moment that felt easy.]

584
00:39:01,780 --> 00:39:04,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't know if "hard"
