585
00:39:05,660 --> 00:39:08,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's just been difficult.]

586
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:11,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Actually, we all find it hard.
Kim Su Min: Of course.]

587
00:39:11,980 --> 00:39:14,500
[Kim Su Min: This is a drinking session,
