588
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:18,820
[Kim Su Min: It's the fifth day.]

589
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:22,180
[Kim Su Min: Have you made up your mind yet?]

590
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:28,780
[An answer that requires courage]

591
00:39:39,100 --> 00:39:41,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yes.]

592
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:46,380
[Kim Su Min: So, you have.
What about you, Han Gyeol?]

593
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:51,540
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm still not sure.]

594
00:39:57,140 --> 00:40:01,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: What about you?
Kim Su Min: Mmm.]

595
00:40:02,100 --> 00:40:04,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah. I'm curious.]

596
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:08,940
[Kim Su Min: No one knows
what will happen tomorrow.]

597
00:40:08,940 --> 00:40:12,340
