601
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:32,260
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

602
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:36,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What about you, Han Gyeol?
Kim Han Gyeol: More than one person.]

603
00:40:36,100 --> 00:40:37,980
[Kim Su Min: More than one?
Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

604
00:40:37,980 --> 00:40:40,060
[Kim Su Min: Well, that's understandable.]

605
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:46,100
[Kim Su Min: As for me? Of course, there's
