607
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:53,460
[Kim Su Min: and want to get to know better.]

608
00:40:54,620 --> 00:40:57,940
[Kim Su Min: I saw
that Hyeok Jin really likes]

609
00:40:57,940 --> 00:41:00,140
[Kim Su Min: Han Gyeol.]

610
00:41:00,140 --> 00:41:03,420
[Kim Su Min: I hoped
they would have a good result.]

611
00:41:03,420 --> 00:41:06,980
[Kim Su Min: So I wanted to lead
their conversation more.]

612
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:10,220
[Kim Su Min: That's why I talked a lot.]

613
00:41:13,220 --> 00:41:17,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: My emotions
fluctuate wildly here.]

614
00:41:17,020 --> 00:41:18,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So it's really exhausting.]

615
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:21,140
[Kim Han Gyeol: My mood changes every hour.]

616
00:41:21,140 --> 00:41:24,420
[Kim Su Min: Every hour? For me, it's every second.
Kim Han Gyeol: Are you okay?]

617
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:27,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know. I was literally crying
and then laughing at the same time,]

618
00:41:28,260 --> 00:41:30,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and that really bothered me.]

619
00:41:32,380 --> 00:41:35,380
[Kim Su Min: What makes you the happiest, then?]

620
00:41:37,140 --> 00:41:41,140
[Kim Su Min: Your happiest moment
in these five days.]

621
00:41:43,580 --> 00:41:47,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: By my standards,
it was the day my heart became clear.]

622
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:52,260
[Kim Su Min: Which day was that?]

623
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:54,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think
it was the third day.]

624
00:41:55,060 --> 00:41:59,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: A certain conversation
made my feelings clear.]

625
00:42:01,460 --> 00:42:06,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Do you have a happiest day?
Kim Su Min: Mmm.]

626
00:42:08,420 --> 00:42:11,660
[Kim Su Min: For me, it's today.]

627
00:42:11,660 --> 00:42:13,380
[Kim Su Min: I'm in a great mood today.]

628
00:42:14,140 --> 00:42:16,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What about Han Gyeol?]

629
00:42:16,580 --> 00:42:20,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: I also became clear...]

630
00:42:20,780 --> 00:42:24,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: Wait. Let me think again.]

631
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:25,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: This question
is always hard to answer.]

632
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:29,580
[Kim Su Min: A day you felt good?]

633
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:31,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.
They were all about the same.]

634
00:42:33,900 --> 00:42:37,420
[Kim Han Gyeol: The day I truly laughed
for the first time.]

635
00:42:37,420 --> 00:42:40,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: The day I laughed brightly.
Kim Su Min: When was that?]

636
00:42:41,220 --> 00:42:42,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's a secret.]

637
00:42:42,940 --> 00:42:44,580
[Kim Su Min: While talking to whom?]

638
00:42:44,940 --> 00:42:48,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't know.
Eum Hyeok Jin: From a certain moment on,
the number of secrets started to grow.]

639
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:51,780
[Kim Su Min: Secrets tend
to pile up here.]

640
00:42:51,780 --> 00:42:53,780
[Kim Su Min: But not really.
Many people are quite straightforward.]

641
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:58,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I am straightforward.
Kim Su Min: I have many secrets.]

642
00:42:58,660 --> 00:43:02,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hyung,
those aren't secrets.]

643
00:43:02,340 --> 00:43:04,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You're just like someone
doing a silent retreat.]

644
00:43:06,660 --> 00:43:10,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: You are quite quiet.]

645
00:43:10,860 --> 00:43:12,500
[Kim Su Min: Do I look like someone
who talks a lot?]

646
00:43:12,500 --> 00:43:14,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.
Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

647
00:43:15,580 --> 00:43:18,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: I felt like you were
very eloquent.]

648
00:43:18,660 --> 00:43:20,460
[Kim Su Min: Really?
Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

649
00:43:20,460 --> 00:43:25,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Then, in your opinion,]

650
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:27,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: do you think the person
you're currently getting close to]

651
00:43:27,620 --> 00:43:33,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and the person you actually like
could end up becoming a couple?]

652
00:43:33,140 --> 00:43:35,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No?
Kim Su Min: No.]

653
00:43:36,380 --> 00:43:39,540
[Kim Su Min: What about you two?]

654
00:43:45,780 --> 00:43:48,260
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't know.]

655
00:43:51,140 --> 00:43:53,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: What about you?]

656
00:43:55,420 --> 00:44:02,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: As for
whether we can become a final couple,]

657
00:44:02,620 --> 00:44:06,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I honestly don't think
that choice is entirely in my hands.]

658
00:44:06,980 --> 00:44:12,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It depends on the other person.]

659
00:44:12,940 --> 00:44:15,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's how it feels.]

660
00:44:18,260 --> 00:44:21,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: He said it depends
on the other person's actions.]

661
00:44:21,620 --> 00:44:23,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: But that person is me.]

662
00:44:23,780 --> 00:44:26,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: Honestly,
that put pressure on me.]

663
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:29,140
[Kim Han Gyeol: I feel a bit of a burden.]

664
00:44:30,020 --> 00:44:32,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: When asked
about becoming a final couple,]

665
00:44:32,020 --> 00:44:34,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Han Gyeol answered first.]

666
00:44:34,620 --> 00:44:36,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He said he didn't know.]

667
00:44:36,740 --> 00:44:38,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That means
it was uncertain.]

668
00:44:39,940 --> 00:44:42,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: After hearing his answer,
my response was...]

669
00:44:42,860 --> 00:44:44,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I said that on purpose.]

670
00:44:44,660 --> 00:44:48,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If you choose me,
we'll be matched.
If you don't, we won't.]

671
00:44:56,340 --> 00:45:01,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: During the day,
it was really fun and exciting.]

672
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:06,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But the night date
was a bit chaotic.]

673
00:45:06,620 --> 00:45:09,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But honestly,
how could it not be?]

674
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:18,700
[When will Hyeok Jin and Han Gyeol's hearts
finally settle down?]

675
00:45:19,620 --> 00:45:22,940
[A night to share feelings comfortably]

676
00:45:23,860 --> 00:45:26,700
[Which couple will drink beer together?]

677
00:45:27,860 --> 00:45:29,340
[Taichi: It's cold.
Cho Yun Jae: Cold?]

678
00:45:29,340 --> 00:45:32,980
[Taichi: Aren't you cold?
Cho Yun Jae: Mmm, I'm okay.]

679
00:45:32,980 --> 00:45:35,460
[Cho Yun Jae: Did you bring a heat pack?
Taichi: No.]

680
00:45:35,460 --> 00:45:37,740
[Cho Yun Jae: I expected it to be Taichi.]

681
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:40,620
[Cho Yun Jae: I also hoped
he would come.]

682
00:45:40,620 --> 00:45:43,260
[Taichi: Although we are
like friends now,]

683
00:45:43,260 --> 00:45:45,380
[Taichi: we get along well, so I chose him.]

684
00:45:45,380 --> 00:45:48,900
[Taichi: But so far,
I don't have romantic feelings.]

685
00:45:48,900 --> 00:45:51,660
[Taichi: I went on the date
to confirm that.]

686
00:45:52,860 --> 00:45:57,180
[Cho Yun Jae: It feels just like Christmas.
Taichi: Exactly.]

687
00:45:59,020 --> 00:46:02,260
[What kind of feelings
will Yun Jae and Taichi share?]

688
00:46:03,340 --> 00:46:07,060
[Taichi: The vibe is so nice.
Cho Yun Jae: Yeah. Don't you like Christmas?]

689
00:46:07,060 --> 00:46:09,260
[Taichi: I do.]

690
00:46:14,180 --> 00:46:17,100
[Taichi: This is delicious.
Cho Yun Jae: Yes.]

691
00:46:17,100 --> 00:46:20,620
[Taichi: That's insane.
Cho Yun Jae: I originally loved snacks.]

692
00:46:20,620 --> 00:46:25,260
[Cho Yun Jae: But I couldn't really
eat them in the Men's House.
Taichi: True. Didn't you bring any?]

693
00:46:25,260 --> 00:46:30,020
[Cho Yun Jae: Uh, actually, I wanted
to go to the convenience store.]

694
00:46:34,540 --> 00:46:39,060
[The beer snacks are served]

695
00:46:39,420 --> 00:46:41,500
[Cheers!]

696
00:46:50,260 --> 00:46:52,420
[Taichi: This is good.
Cho Yun Jae: Good.]

697
00:46:52,420 --> 00:46:55,140
[Taichi: How is it?
Cho Yun Jae: What do you want to ask?]

698
00:46:55,540 --> 00:46:58,460
[Taichi: After all, this is
our first time out on a date.]

699
00:46:58,740 --> 00:47:01,100
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm already finding it fun.]

700
00:47:01,700 --> 00:47:03,340
[Taichi: I'm having fun too.]

701
00:47:03,340 --> 00:47:05,980
[Cho Yun Jae: I find it fun just
looking at your face.]

702
00:47:07,620 --> 00:47:11,300
[Taichi: Are you drunk already?
Cho Yun Jae: No.]

703
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:14,140
[The conversation continues
in a comfortable vibe]

704
00:47:14,860 --> 00:47:21,820
[Cho Yun Jae: So, how does it feel?
It is our first time going out together, after all.
Taichi: I find it fun too.]

705
00:47:21,820 --> 00:47:23,460
[Taichi: I've been on a few outings before.]

706
00:47:23,460 --> 00:47:24,820
[Taichi: This is the first time talking
has felt this easy.]

707
00:47:26,020 --> 00:47:28,100
[Taichi: Before, it was a bit awkward.
I didn't know what to say.]

708
00:47:28,100 --> 00:47:30,940
[Taichi: It's fun not having to think
about those things.]

709
00:47:40,780 --> 00:47:45,780
[Cho Yun Jae: Being like friends is a good thing.
Taichi: Yes.]

710
00:47:46,140 --> 00:47:49,780
[Taichi: Anything you want to ask?
Cho Yun Jae: Anything I want to ask?]

711
00:47:50,180 --> 00:47:51,980
[Cho Yun Jae: What was
your first impression of me?]

712
00:47:53,660 --> 00:47:55,100
[Taichi: I really thought
you were younger than me.]

713
00:47:56,660 --> 00:47:59,100
[Taichi: Because before I joined,
I thought I'd definitely be the youngest,]

714
00:47:59,100 --> 00:48:02,020
[Taichi: since I'm young.]

715
00:48:02,020 --> 00:48:05,060
[Taichi: I thought you were even younger.
Cho Yun Jae: Ah.]

716
00:48:05,060 --> 00:48:06,460
[Taichi: Why is your skin so good?]

717
00:48:06,460 --> 00:48:09,460
[Cho Yun Jae: Well.
But your skin is great, too.]

718
00:48:09,460 --> 00:48:11,900
[Taichi: If I take off my makeup,
I have bad spots.]

719
00:48:11,900 --> 00:48:13,540
[Taichi: But you look exactly the same
even without it.]

720
00:48:13,540 --> 00:48:15,940
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't wear makeup.
Taichi: Seriously?]

721
00:48:15,940 --> 00:48:20,380
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah. I only put on sunscreen today.
Taichi: Wow, is there a secret?
Did you do anything special?]

722
00:48:20,380 --> 00:48:21,540
[Cho Yun Jae: Nothing.]

723
00:48:20,980 --> 00:48:21,540
Nothing?

724
00:48:21,980 --> 00:48:25,260
[Cho Yun Jae: I usually sleep
for a long time and drink a lot of water.]

725
00:48:25,540 --> 00:48:28,100
[Cho Yun Jae: But I haven't slept much
since coming here.]

726
00:48:29,060 --> 00:48:30,220
[Taichi: How many hours
do you usually sleep?]

727
00:48:31,580 --> 00:48:34,580
[Cho Yun Jae: 12 hours.]

728
00:48:35,260 --> 00:48:38,140
[Taichi: Then what was
your first impression of me?]

729
00:48:38,140 --> 00:48:40,260
[Cho Yun Jae: I didn't expect you
to be Japanese.]

730
00:48:40,260 --> 00:48:41,900
[Taichi: Ah, really?
Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

731
00:48:41,900 --> 00:48:45,820
[Taichi: Where do you think I'm from?
Cho Yun Jae: Before you spoke,]

732
00:48:45,820 --> 00:48:48,900
[Cho Yun Jae: I thought
you were Korean.]

733
00:48:48,900 --> 00:48:50,460
[Taichi: Should I have stayed quiet?]

734
00:48:50,460 --> 00:48:55,260
[Cho Yun Jae: Also, you look super fair.
Seriously, really fair.]

735
00:48:55,260 --> 00:48:57,540
[Taichi: That's the first time
I've heard that.]

736
00:48:57,540 --> 00:49:00,580
[Cho Yun Jae: But anyway,
our worry is the same.]

737
00:49:00,580 --> 00:49:04,740
[Cho Yun Jae: We have fun
and it's interesting when we're together.]

738
00:49:04,740 --> 00:49:09,460
[Cho Yun Jae: But can we actually
take it a step further?]

739
00:49:09,460 --> 00:49:13,100
[Cho Yun Jae: We are both struggling
with that question.]

740
00:49:13,700 --> 00:49:15,660
[Cho Yun Jae: So it was right
to come out.]

741
00:49:15,660 --> 00:49:20,020
[Cho Yun Jae: If I have an opportunity
like this, I'll definitely take it.]

742
00:49:20,020 --> 00:49:24,300
[Taichi: Me too.]

743
00:49:24,300 --> 00:49:26,260
[Taichi: I hadn't cleared
my thoughts back then, either.]

744
00:49:26,260 --> 00:49:28,980
[Taichi: But I want to ask one thing.]

745
00:49:28,980 --> 00:49:30,820
[Taichi: Can you actually see me
in a romantic way?]

746
00:49:30,820 --> 00:49:33,740
[Taichi: I want to confirm that first.]

747
00:49:34,300 --> 00:49:37,500
[Taichi: Do you think we can develop
into something romantic later?]

748
00:49:38,420 --> 00:49:42,100
[Cho Yun Jae: Honestly, I don't know.]

749
00:49:42,380 --> 00:49:45,460
[Cho Yun Jae: The time has been too short—]

750
00:49:45,460 --> 00:49:49,380
[Cho Yun Jae: We can't decide]

751
00:49:49,380 --> 00:49:53,820
[Cho Yun Jae: whether this is just
friendship based on that alone, right?
Taichi: Yeah.]

752
00:49:53,820 --> 00:49:56,980
[Cho Yun Jae: That's why I feel confused.]

753
00:49:57,540 --> 00:50:01,820
[Taichi: When you came to see me yesterday,
I was straightforward.]

754
00:50:03,020 --> 00:50:06,780
[Taichi: This is the first time
I've gotten along with someone this well.]

755
00:50:06,780 --> 00:50:09,100
[Taichi: On a first date,
if we don't click.]

756
00:50:09,100 --> 00:50:11,380
[Taichi: I wouldn't see them again.
That's my personality.]

757
00:50:11,380 --> 00:50:14,940
[Taichi: I make up my mind quickly
because it's easier.]

758
00:50:16,860 --> 00:50:20,620
[Taichi: That's why I didn't choose you]

759
00:50:20,620 --> 00:50:22,100
[Taichi: after the first day.]

760
00:50:22,700 --> 00:50:24,420
[Taichi: Because on the first day,
to be honest,]

761
00:50:24,420 --> 00:50:27,420
[Taichi: it wasn't a date that was fun
or had romantic feelings for me.]

762
00:50:27,420 --> 00:50:30,260
[Taichi: So I thought we probably
weren't a match.]

763
00:50:30,260 --> 00:50:31,540
[Taichi: And that was that.]

764
00:50:32,060 --> 00:50:35,180
[Taichi: But after continuing to talk to you,]

765
00:50:35,180 --> 00:50:38,900
[Taichi: even though we haven't known
each other long, we click so well]

766
00:50:38,900 --> 00:50:40,660
[Taichi: and have so many things
in common.]

767
00:50:40,660 --> 00:50:43,220
[Taichi: I haven't met someone
this easy and fun to talk to in a long time.]

768
00:50:43,620 --> 00:50:47,100
[Hearing Taichi's true feelings
for the first time]

769
00:50:47,100 --> 00:50:49,460
[Taichi: But like I said, up until now,
I'm still not sure]

770
00:50:49,460 --> 00:50:54,020
[Taichi: whether this feeling is just
friendly affection or something more—]

771
00:50:54,020 --> 00:50:55,300
[Taichi: like romantic attraction
toward a woman or a man.]

772
00:50:55,740 --> 00:50:57,500
[Taichi: And you also said
you aren't sure.]

773
00:50:57,500 --> 00:51:00,140
[Taichi: After coming out like this today,
what do you think?]

774
00:51:00,140 --> 00:51:05,900
[Cho Yun Jae: Actually, that's the part]

775
00:51:05,900 --> 00:51:07,180
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm most uncertain about.]

776
00:51:07,180 --> 00:51:11,540
[Cho Yun Jae: Because we didn't meet
as a man and a woman,]

777
00:51:11,540 --> 00:51:13,860
[Cho Yun Jae: but as two guys,]

778
00:51:13,860 --> 00:51:17,860
[Cho Yun Jae: the line between friendship
and romance was already kind of blurred.]

779
00:51:17,860 --> 00:51:21,260
[Cho Yun Jae: So I don't have that standard.]

780
00:51:21,260 --> 00:51:24,220
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm not sure yet.]

781
00:51:24,220 --> 00:51:28,340
[Cho Yun Jae: But anyway,
there are two days left.]

782
00:51:28,620 --> 00:51:32,620
[Cho Yun Jae: I should think
and consider it carefully.]

783
00:51:33,860 --> 00:51:38,580
[Taichi: But there's one thing
I want to tell you first.]

784
00:51:38,580 --> 00:51:41,980
[Taichi: At this stage,]

785
00:51:42,460 --> 00:51:46,300
[Taichi: I don't think it's romantic liking yet.
Cho Yun Jae: I see.]

786
00:51:46,940 --> 00:51:49,780
[Taichi: That is my most honest thought.]

787
00:51:49,780 --> 00:51:57,380
[Cho Yun Jae: I can understand.
I feel about the same.]

788
00:52:00,500 --> 00:52:03,780
[Taichi: Honestly, even up to now,
when we eat together]

789
00:52:03,780 --> 00:52:07,940
[Taichi: and really hit it off
and have great conversations,]

790
00:52:07,940 --> 00:52:09,340
[Taichi: it still feels more like
being close friends]

791
00:52:09,340 --> 00:52:11,980
[Taichi: than romantic feelings.]

792
00:52:11,980 --> 00:52:15,780
[Taichi: But I'm grateful he said]

793
00:52:15,780 --> 00:52:18,020
[Taichi: there's a possibility.]

794
00:52:18,020 --> 00:52:20,940
[Cho Yun Jae: He's different from
what I thought.]

795
00:52:20,940 --> 00:52:24,820
[Cho Yun Jae: I originally just saw him
as a younger friend.]

796
00:52:24,820 --> 00:52:29,380
[Cho Yun Jae: But I realized
he's more mature than I thought.]

797
00:52:29,380 --> 00:52:31,620
[Cho Yun Jae: He has many thoughts.]

798
00:52:31,620 --> 00:52:34,420
[Cho Yun Jae: Although I've
processed it somewhat,]

799
00:52:34,420 --> 00:52:38,740
[Cho Yun Jae: I still don't have]

800
00:52:38,740 --> 00:52:42,700
[Cho Yun Jae: a clear answer.]

801
00:52:43,540 --> 00:52:48,580
[Cho Yun Jae: Then what do you think will
happen between me and Hyun Jun?]

802
00:52:48,580 --> 00:52:52,300
[Taichi: Shouldn't you be more proactive
and do something?]

803
00:52:52,300 --> 00:52:57,020
[Cho Yun Jae: If I had been proactive
from day one,]

804
00:52:57,020 --> 00:52:59,020
[Cho Yun Jae: things might have been different.]

805
00:52:59,020 --> 00:53:03,620
[Cho Yun Jae: But I only decided]

806
00:53:03,620 --> 00:53:05,540
[Cho Yun Jae: to be proactive yesterday
or the day before,]

807
00:53:05,540 --> 00:53:08,340
[Cho Yun Jae: meaning half the time
is already gone.]

808
00:53:08,340 --> 00:53:13,860
[Cho Yun Jae: So I feel like even if
I do something, nothing will change.]

809
00:53:13,860 --> 00:53:18,060
[Cho Yun Jae: And honestly, Sun Wook
and I are good friends.]

810
00:53:18,340 --> 00:53:22,580
[Cho Yun Jae: So it feels harder
to just approach carelessly.]

811
00:53:22,580 --> 00:53:25,980
[Taichi: But this isn't a show
for making friends.]

812
00:53:27,940 --> 00:53:32,060
[Cho Yun Jae: Still, I don't want
to make Hyun Jun uncomfortable.]

813
00:53:32,060 --> 00:53:34,660
[Taichi: He might not feel uncomfortable.]

814
00:53:35,060 --> 00:53:38,300
[Taichi: Maybe he's waiting]

815
00:53:38,300 --> 00:53:40,060
[Taichi: for you to be more proactive.]

816
00:53:40,060 --> 00:53:42,820
[Cho Yun Jae: What do you think
the probability of that is?]

817
00:53:43,020 --> 00:53:46,500
[Taichi: I'm not sure.
I don't think that's really my place to say.]

818
00:53:46,500 --> 00:53:49,260
[Taichi: Because that's just
my personal judgment.]

819
00:53:52,180 --> 00:53:54,740
[Taichi: But what I want to tell you is—]

820
00:53:54,740 --> 00:53:56,300
[Taichi: If you like him,]

821
00:53:56,300 --> 00:53:59,740
[Taichi: I hope you don't regret
these feelings later.]

822
00:54:00,300 --> 00:54:03,780
[Taichi: Anyway, you had the courage
to come on this show.]

823
00:54:03,780 --> 00:54:06,660
[Taichi: And everyone knows
we are in a position]

824
00:54:06,660 --> 00:54:09,420
[Taichi: where we have to compete,]

825
00:54:09,420 --> 00:54:11,260
[Taichi: so they will all understand you]

826
00:54:11,260 --> 00:54:14,900
[Taichi: and won't hate you.]

827
00:54:16,020 --> 00:54:18,340
[Cho Yun Jae: Then I'll try harder.]

828
00:54:18,340 --> 00:54:21,460
[Taichi: I think if you want to do something,
you should just do it.]

829
00:54:21,460 --> 00:54:23,460
[Taichi: Because you might not
get another chance,]

830
00:54:23,460 --> 00:54:24,980
[Taichi: and you don't know if you'll be able
to see Hyun Jun again afterwards.]

831
00:54:26,540 --> 00:54:29,860
[Cho Yun Jae: No one knows
how things will change.]

832
00:54:29,860 --> 00:54:31,700
[Taichi: Will you not do it just
because you don't know?]

833
00:54:31,700 --> 00:54:34,220
[Cho Yun Jae: No. I have to do it.
Taichi: Exactly.]

834
00:54:34,220 --> 00:54:37,500
[Taichi: Even if you see it as a drawback,
there's no benefit to dwelling on it. ]

835
00:54:37,500 --> 00:54:39,860
[Taichi: If you think you did well,]

836
00:54:39,860 --> 00:54:44,100
[Taichi: you can allow yourself to feel hopeful.
It was 70:30 before, but now it's improved—]

837
00:54:44,100 --> 00:54:47,180
[Taichi: You just need to try a little harder.
After all, there are still two days left.]

838
00:54:48,780 --> 00:54:50,900
[Cho Yun Jae: Cheer for me.]

839
00:54:51,380 --> 00:54:53,660
[Taichi: Okay.]

840
00:54:56,180 --> 00:54:59,820
[The two share their inner thoughts]

841
00:55:00,340 --> 00:55:04,420
[Will they find the love of their dreams?]

842
00:55:05,970 --> 00:55:10,410
[The night falls. Which couple
will feel the heart-fluttering together?]

843
00:55:10,940 --> 00:55:11,660
Over here.

844
00:55:12,810 --> 00:55:19,330
[Lee Hyun Jun: Where are we going? Do you know?
Kim Sun Wook: No. How about we go to eat?]

845
00:55:19,330 --> 00:55:23,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: Sun Wook has also been continuously
making moves on me since the second day.]

846
00:55:23,810 --> 00:55:26,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: So I was curious about his thoughts.
I felt it would be better to come over,]

847
00:55:27,330 --> 00:55:29,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: because I was really looking forward
to knowing what was going on in his heart.]

848
00:55:29,570 --> 00:55:32,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: That feeling was pretty strong.]

849
00:55:32,450 --> 00:55:36,690
[Kim Sun Wook: I asked
to meet Hyun Jun tonight.]

850
00:55:36,690 --> 00:55:38,810
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought a night date
would be fun.]

851
00:55:38,810 --> 00:55:40,930
[Kim Sun Wook: So I was very happy.]

852
00:55:41,730 --> 00:55:45,170
[Kim Sun Wook: Shall we go in?
Lee Hyun Jun: Sure.]

853
00:55:45,570 --> 00:55:49,970
[Kim Sun Wook: Mmm.
Lee Hyun Jun: Foxes. There are many foxes.]

854
00:55:49,970 --> 00:55:53,090
[Kim Sun Wook: The vibe is really good.]

855
00:55:53,410 --> 00:55:57,610
[A great vibe to focus on each other]

856
00:55:58,130 --> 00:56:01,650
[Plus cute fox characters
adding to the fun]

857
00:56:02,730 --> 00:56:05,130
[Lee Hyun Jun: The foxes are cute.]

858
00:56:05,130 --> 00:56:09,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: What do you want to eat?
Kim Sun Wook: Pork belly
with bean sprouts sounds good.]

859
00:56:09,890 --> 00:56:12,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: Jamón.
Kim Sun Wook: Jamón?]

860
00:56:12,650 --> 00:56:16,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: Drinks?
Kim Sun Wook: How about cocktails?]

861
00:56:17,770 --> 00:56:21,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: How was today?
Kim Sun Wook: Today?]

862
00:56:21,170 --> 00:56:25,810
[Kim Sun Wook: We jumped.
Lee Hyun Jun: Bungee jumping?]

863
00:56:25,810 --> 00:56:27,410
[Lee Hyun Jun: How?]

864
00:56:27,410 --> 00:56:30,730
[Kim Sun Wook: Just coming down together
from the top.]

865
00:56:30,730 --> 00:56:34,090
[Lee Hyun Jun: That sounds fun.
Kim Sun Wook: It was. What about you?]

866
00:56:34,450 --> 00:56:39,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: I went to the jacuzzi
and outdoor sauna.]

867
00:56:39,170 --> 00:56:40,690
[Kim Sun Wook: Did you
take your clothes off?]

868
00:56:40,690 --> 00:56:42,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was taken off.]

869
00:56:44,730 --> 00:56:47,370
[Kim Sun Wook: Ah, I haven't
seen that yet...]

870
00:56:52,370 --> 00:56:55,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do you like amusement park rides?
Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

871
00:56:55,010 --> 00:56:59,530
[Kim Sun Wook: But I probably
wouldn't do bungee jumping.
Lee Hyun Jun: I'd like to try it.]

872
00:56:59,530 --> 00:57:02,130
[Kim Sun Wook: Haven't you tried it?
Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

873
00:57:02,130 --> 00:57:04,370
[Kim Sun Wook: If you jump, I'll jump too.
Lee Hyun Jun: Oh, I'm a man of my word.]

874
00:57:04,370 --> 00:57:05,770
[Kim Sun Wook: I am, too.]

875
00:57:05,770 --> 00:57:06,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: Then let's do it.
Kim Sun Wook: Okay.]

876
00:57:06,970 --> 00:57:07,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: Pfft.]

877
00:57:07,890 --> 00:57:10,370
[Kim Sun Wook: What are you "pffting" at?]

878
00:57:11,290 --> 00:57:13,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a deal then.]

879
00:57:13,930 --> 00:57:16,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: No backing out.
Kim Sun Wook: Okay.]

880
00:57:17,970 --> 00:57:21,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a promise. We sealed it.
Kim Sun Wook: Okay.]

881
00:57:21,490 --> 00:57:24,610
[Kim Sun Wook: I can really do it.
That's nothing.]

882
00:57:30,340 --> 00:57:32,980
[Stiff]

883
00:57:36,530 --> 00:57:38,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why are you so stiff?]

884
00:57:38,290 --> 00:57:39,980
[Kim Sun Wook: Me? No. I'm just hungry.]

885
00:57:39,980 --> 00:57:41,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: Are you?
Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

886
00:57:41,650 --> 00:57:47,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: Eat everything later then.
Kim Sun Wook: Everything? Is this a mukbang?]

887
00:57:47,170 --> 00:57:57,010
[Kim Sun Wook: Was tonight about contacting
the one whose true feelings you're curious about?
Lee Hyun Jun: Yes.]

888
00:57:57,010 --> 00:57:59,090
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm curious
about your true feelings...]

889
00:57:59,090 --> 00:58:02,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: Mine?
Kim Sun Wook: Of course.]

890
00:58:02,810 --> 00:58:06,650
[Kim Sun Wook: After all, I haven't heard them.
Lee Hyun Jun: That's true.]

891
00:58:06,650 --> 00:58:10,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: But I think I need
a drink before I speak.
Kim Sun Wook: Ah, I see.]

892
00:58:11,450 --> 00:58:17,690
[Kim Sun Wook: I think hoodies suit you well.
Lee Hyun Jun: This hoodie? I just bought it.]

893
00:58:17,690 --> 00:58:19,250
[Kim Sun Wook: It looks good on you.]

894
00:58:19,250 --> 00:58:21,730
[Kim Sun Wook: It's a heart.]

895
00:58:23,010 --> 00:58:25,090
[Lee Hyun Jun: Thanks.]

896
00:58:26,650 --> 00:58:31,850
[Kim Sun Wook: Do you usually
give such short answers?
Lee Hyun Jun: Mmm. A bit.]

897
00:58:32,330 --> 00:58:36,090
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'm usually like this.
What's wrong?]

898
00:58:36,090 --> 00:58:40,370
[Kim Sun Wook: This is good.
That "Mmm" just now was good.]

899
00:58:40,370 --> 00:58:41,730
[Kim Sun Wook: It has that vibe.]

900
00:58:42,650 --> 00:58:44,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: How should...
how should I answer?]

901
00:58:44,010 --> 00:58:46,770
[Kim Sun Wook: "Thank you."
Lee Hyun Jun: Thank you.]

902
00:58:47,170 --> 00:58:53,850
[Kim Sun Wook: It's not that it's bad.
At first, it made it a bit hard to talk to you.
Lee Hyun Jun: Like, "Why does he talk so short?"]

903
00:58:53,850 --> 00:58:56,970
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah. Like you
only give simple answers.]

904
00:58:57,530 --> 00:59:01,770
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought it meant
"Don't talk to me."]

905
00:59:01,770 --> 00:59:05,250
[Kim Sun Wook: But now I see
you didn't mean it that way.]

906
00:59:06,650 --> 00:59:09,250
[Lee Hyun Jun: My answers are too short...]

907
00:59:09,650 --> 00:59:12,570
[I'll try to fix it.]

908
00:59:12,660 --> 00:59:13,980
I'll try to fix it.

909
00:59:14,380 --> 00:59:15,940
[Uh!]

910
00:59:15,980 --> 00:59:18,330
[Kim Sun Wook: Uh, uh.]

911
00:59:18,330 --> 00:59:21,050
[Kim Sun Wook: I didn't mean it like that.]

912
00:59:30,850 --> 00:59:36,050
[Drinks and food are ready.
Let's have a deep conversation]

913
00:59:36,300 --> 00:59:38,300
[Cheers.]

914
00:59:57,930 --> 01:00:00,890
[Kim Sun Wook: It's already
the fifth day.]

915
01:00:00,890 --> 01:00:03,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: It feels like time passes slowly,
but it's actually fast.]

916
01:00:03,770 --> 01:00:05,290
[Kim Sun Wook: I think it's passed quickly.]

917
01:00:05,290 --> 01:00:08,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: Quickly?
Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

918
01:00:08,850 --> 01:00:10,730
[Kim Sun Wook: How do you feel?]

919
01:00:12,570 --> 01:00:14,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: About what?
Kim Sun Wook: Just everything.]

920
01:00:14,290 --> 01:00:17,330
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think it's all been good.
Quite fun.]

921
01:00:17,330 --> 01:00:20,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's not over yet,
but I'm already satisfied.]

922
01:00:20,930 --> 01:00:22,490
[Kim Sun Wook: I think it's been good, too.]

923
01:00:22,490 --> 01:00:26,370
[Kim Sun Wook: Whether it's dating you
or being here right now.]

924
01:00:26,890 --> 01:00:30,970
[Kim Sun Wook: Yesterday was fun, too.
Lee Hyun Jun: Bowling?]

925
01:00:30,970 --> 01:00:34,010
[Kim Sun Wook: Because I could
see more of your expressions.]

926
01:00:34,610 --> 01:00:37,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: What kind of face
was I making yesterday?]

927
01:00:40,410 --> 01:00:45,250
[The way you laughed. It was really cute.]

928
01:00:54,740 --> 01:00:57,020
[Playing dumb]

929
01:01:00,050 --> 01:01:02,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: I used to be a bartender.]

930
01:01:02,290 --> 01:01:05,370
[Kim Sun Wook: Ah, really?
Lee Hyun Jun: Near Konkuk University.]

931
01:01:05,370 --> 01:01:08,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: Memorizing recipes was exhausting.
Kim Sun Wook: There must be so many.]

932
01:01:08,850 --> 01:01:10,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

933
01:01:10,650 --> 01:01:14,730
[Lee Hyun Jun: But I have a good memory.]

934
01:01:14,730 --> 01:01:18,290
[Kim Sun Wook: My memory is really bad.]

935
01:01:18,290 --> 01:01:19,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: I feel like you
have a good one.]

936
01:01:19,620 --> 01:01:21,540
[Kim Sun Wook: What?
Lee Hyun Jun: I think you have a good memory.]

937
01:01:21,540 --> 01:01:25,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: I was surprised
you remembered my birthday.]

938
01:01:26,530 --> 01:01:30,130
[How could I forget?]

939
01:01:33,220 --> 01:01:34,820
[Shaking]

940
01:01:35,560 --> 01:01:38,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why are your hands shaking so much?
Kim Sun Wook: What?]

941
01:01:38,520 --> 01:01:42,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: I thought there was
an earthquake.]

942
01:01:42,360 --> 01:01:44,840
[Kim Sun Wook: It wasn't like this
during the day.]

943
01:01:44,840 --> 01:01:47,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: They weren't shaking?
Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

944
01:01:47,600 --> 01:01:49,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: They're shaking so hard.]

945
01:01:49,840 --> 01:01:53,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Seeing him so shy
made me want to tease him.]

946
01:01:53,240 --> 01:01:56,000
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do your hands shake
when you're nervous?]

947
01:01:56,000 --> 01:01:58,720
[Kim Sun Wook: Nervous?
Rather than nervous,]

948
01:01:58,720 --> 01:02:01,280
[Kim Sun Wook: they shake
because my heart is fluttering.]

949
01:02:05,400 --> 01:02:08,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why are you getting shy
while saying that yourself?]

950
01:02:09,280 --> 01:02:11,280
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't know.]

951
01:02:12,600 --> 01:02:16,120
[Kim Sun Wook: But I'm always like this
with someone I like.]

952
01:02:16,120 --> 01:02:18,440
[Kim Sun Wook: If I don't like them,
I won't do anything.]

953
01:02:19,360 --> 01:02:20,680
[Lee Hyun Jun: Actually, he's quite cute.]

954
01:02:20,680 --> 01:02:23,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: When everyone is together,
he completely ignores me.]

955
01:02:23,360 --> 01:02:25,160
[Lee Hyun Jun: That part is
actually a bit cute.]

956
01:02:25,400 --> 01:02:29,440
[The conversation between the two heats up]

957
01:02:30,080 --> 01:02:33,680
[Kim Sun Wook: So what are you thinking?]

958
01:02:33,680 --> 01:02:36,600
[Lee Hyun Jun: Can I ask you first?]

959
01:02:36,600 --> 01:02:40,520
[Kim Sun Wook: Didn't I ask you first?
Lee Hyun Jun: Can't I ask first?]

960
01:02:41,720 --> 01:02:44,340
[Lee Hyun Jun: What's on your mind?
Kim Sun Wook: On my mind?]

961
01:02:49,380 --> 01:02:51,260
[I like you.]

962
01:02:51,260 --> 01:02:53,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why?
Kim Sun Wook: What?]

963
01:02:53,760 --> 01:02:55,000
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why do you like me?]

964
01:02:56,160 --> 01:03:03,320
[Kim Sun Wook: You seem sincere
in how you treat people. You're polite. And...]

965
01:03:03,600 --> 01:03:06,000
[Kim Sun Wook: You're handsome.]

966
01:03:08,560 --> 01:03:10,860
[Kim Sun Wook: You're cuter
than I imagined.]

967
01:03:10,860 --> 01:03:11,580
[Kim Sun Wook: That is important.]

968
01:03:12,180 --> 01:03:14,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: How am I cute?
Kim Sun Wook: You're just cuter than I thought.]

969
01:03:14,080 --> 01:03:17,000
[Kim Sun Wook: For example, you like Pikachu.]

970
01:03:17,920 --> 01:03:20,600
[Lee Hyun Jun: Pikachu.]

971
01:03:20,600 --> 01:03:24,920
[Kim Sun Wook: And how you seem a bit shy.
That's cute, too.]

972
01:03:30,600 --> 01:03:33,520
[That's why I like you.]

973
01:03:34,640 --> 01:03:37,040
[Kim Sun Wook: I feel like I made it
way too obvious that I like him—]

974
01:03:37,040 --> 01:03:41,560
[Kim Sun Wook: how I feel
and what I like about him.]

975
01:03:41,560 --> 01:03:42,880
[Kim Sun Wook: I think I said too much.]

976
01:03:42,880 --> 01:03:46,780
[Kim Sun Wook: But that made me feel]

977
01:03:46,780 --> 01:03:49,260
[Kim Sun Wook: a bit embarrassed.]

978
01:03:54,360 --> 01:03:58,080
[Kim Sun Wook: What about you?
Lee Hyun Jun: Me?]

979
01:04:08,360 --> 01:04:13,040
[I like you, too.]

980
01:04:14,840 --> 01:04:20,040
[Lee Hyun Jun: You really like me,
and you're kind.]

981
01:04:20,040 --> 01:04:22,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: You think of me first.
I see all of that.]

982
01:04:27,480 --> 01:04:33,480
[Lee Hyun Jun: I know you're always
considering me, so I...]

983
01:04:33,480 --> 01:04:37,840
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm glad you noticed.]

984
01:04:37,840 --> 01:04:41,320
[Lee Hyun Jun: You did it on purpose.]

985
01:04:42,080 --> 01:04:44,840
[Kim Sun Wook: Someone once said
if you're going to do it, you have to show it.]

986
01:04:44,840 --> 01:04:48,480
[Lee Hyun Jun: And I was a bit touched
on the second day,]

987
01:04:49,360 --> 01:04:54,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: you took me to the room
and gave me a card.]

988
01:04:54,360 --> 01:04:56,280
[Lee Hyun Jun: That really touched me.
Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

989
01:04:56,280 --> 01:04:59,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: You kept the card I gave you,
and on it,]

990
01:04:59,960 --> 01:05:02,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: you wrote your feelings
and gave it back to me.]

991
01:05:04,040 --> 01:05:06,400
[Lee Hyun Jun: That also touched me.]

992
01:05:07,880 --> 01:05:12,320
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think
that was my most touched moment.
Kim Sun Wook: Ah, really?]

993
01:05:12,320 --> 01:05:19,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: "Ah, he cares about me this much."
Kim Sun Wook: Yes. Exactly.]

994
01:05:19,080 --> 01:05:22,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: The same goes
for the gifts and letters.]

995
01:05:22,240 --> 01:05:26,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: Compared to what you prepared,
mine seems so thoughtless.]

996
01:05:26,520 --> 01:05:32,880
[Lee Hyun Jun: The letters and gifts
you gave me really touched me.]

997
01:05:34,200 --> 01:05:36,720
[Kim Sun Wook: But I could also feel it.
Lee Hyun Jun: What?]

998
01:05:36,720 --> 01:05:38,960
[Kim Sun Wook: You have feelings for me.]

999
01:05:39,720 --> 01:05:43,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Oh, so you felt it.]

1000
01:05:43,240 --> 01:05:46,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: I thought you didn't.
Kim Sun Wook: I could feel everything.]

1001
01:05:46,960 --> 01:05:53,200
[Kim Sun Wook: But I felt like you wouldn't
be proactive, so I approached you first.]

1002
01:05:53,200 --> 01:05:55,720
[Kim Sun Wook: But I'm really
not the proactive type.]

1003
01:05:55,720 --> 01:05:57,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: Ah, really?]

1004
01:05:58,000 --> 01:06:05,480
[Kim Sun Wook: If I like or am interested
in someone, I pretend I don't care.
Lee Hyun Jun: I could tell.]

1005
01:06:05,480 --> 01:06:13,480
[Kim Sun Wook: If it's 1-on-1, I'll approach,
but I'm too scared when there are many people.]

1006
01:06:14,120 --> 01:06:19,440
[Kim Sun Wook: I'll just treat him
as if he's invisible.
Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah. You treated me like that—]

1007
01:06:19,440 --> 01:06:23,280
[Lee Hyun Jun: like it didn't matter whether
I was there or not, or whether I'd eaten or not.]

1008
01:06:23,640 --> 01:06:27,200
[Kim Sun Wook: But that really wasn't my intention.
Lee Hyun Jun: I know.]

1009
01:06:27,200 --> 01:06:30,480
[Kim Sun Wook: Mmm. You understand now, right?
I didn't truly mean it.]

1010
01:06:31,760 --> 01:06:37,040
[Lee Hyun Jun: It was like two days ago,
when we were having drinks and playing Jenga.
You said it, didn't you?]

1011
01:06:37,040 --> 01:06:42,960
[Kim Sun Wook: Said what?
Lee Hyun Jun: You said you had never been proactive.]

1012
01:06:42,960 --> 01:06:45,680
[Kim Sun Wook: It wasn't during the game.]

1013
01:06:45,680 --> 01:06:49,640
[Kim Sun Wook: It must have been
when it was just a few of us.]

1014
01:06:50,200 --> 01:06:55,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: Anyway, hearing that back then,]

1015
01:06:55,520 --> 01:07:00,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: I realized then—
he really does like me.]

1016
01:07:00,360 --> 01:07:02,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: You've never been like this before.]

1017
01:07:02,240 --> 01:07:05,200
[Lee Hyun Jun: But now
you're expressing it so proactively.]

1018
01:07:05,680 --> 01:07:08,760
[Kim Sun Wook: But once I like someone,]

1019
01:07:09,080 --> 01:07:15,860
[Kim Sun Wook: I get very invested.]

1020
01:07:15,860 --> 01:07:18,980
[Kim Sun Wook: That's why I'm like this now.]

1021
01:07:23,840 --> 01:07:26,580
[Lee Hyun Jun: Suddenly, you can't
look me in the eye.]

1022
01:07:30,940 --> 01:07:35,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: I can feel how much he cares about me.
I'm grateful for his thoughtfulness.]

1023
01:07:35,660 --> 01:07:37,740
[Lee Hyun Jun: Since he expressed
his feelings for me,]

1024
01:07:37,740 --> 01:07:40,920
[Lee Hyun Jun: I told him how I feel, too.]

1025
01:07:40,920 --> 01:07:43,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: I expressed my feelings
to Sun Wook.]

1026
01:07:43,220 --> 01:07:45,460
[Lee Hyun Jun: I don't know
how Sun Wook felt about it.]

1027
01:07:45,860 --> 01:07:48,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: But I can clearly feel]

1028
01:07:48,660 --> 01:07:52,060
[Lee Hyun Jun: he cares about me
more than anyone else.]

1029
01:07:53,000 --> 01:07:57,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: And I realized
he really values me.]

1030
01:08:00,960 --> 01:08:06,040
[That night, they spoke in an unhurried way,
laying their hearts bare to one another]

1031
01:08:06,040 --> 01:08:09,760
[Kim Sun Wook: How do you feel
after hearing my inner thoughts?]

1032
01:08:09,760 --> 01:08:12,800
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'm touched.
Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

1033
01:08:12,800 --> 01:08:14,400
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yes.
Kim Sun Wook: Okay.]

1034
01:08:14,400 --> 01:08:17,040
[Kim Sun Wook: You think that
because you're a good person.]

1035
01:08:17,040 --> 01:08:20,160
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've never thought of myself
as a good person.]

1036
01:08:21,279 --> 01:08:24,279
[Kim Sun Wook: No way.]

1037
01:08:25,080 --> 01:08:28,040
[Kim Sun Wook: Don't think like that.]

1038
01:08:28,040 --> 01:08:30,560
[Lee Hyun Jun:If you say so, then I'll take it.
Kim Sun Wook: Well.]

1039
01:08:30,560 --> 01:08:34,000
[Kim Sun Wook: To me, you are a good person.]

1040
01:08:36,600 --> 01:08:40,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've never thought
of myself as a good person.]

1041
01:08:41,120 --> 01:08:44,200
[Lee Hyun Jun: But hearing Sun Wook
say he thinks so,]

1042
01:08:44,200 --> 01:08:47,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: I was truly touched.]

1043
01:08:47,240 --> 01:08:52,640
[Lee Hyun Jun: After hearing Sun Wook's thoughts,
I'm even more certain of my feelings.]

1044
01:08:52,640 --> 01:08:58,279
[Kim Sun Wook: Honestly, I don't really remember]

1045
01:08:58,680 --> 01:09:01,160
[Kim Sun Wook: what Hyun Jun thinks of me.
Because...]

1046
01:09:01,160 --> 01:09:05,520
[Kim Sun Wook: I care about him so much.
I was so blatant that I surprised myself.]

1047
01:09:05,520 --> 01:09:09,359
[Kim Sun Wook: So, to be honest,
I don't really have an impression]

1048
01:09:09,359 --> 01:09:12,920
[Kim Sun Wook: of what he thinks of me.]

1049
01:09:14,479 --> 01:09:21,080
[That night's heart-fluttering date.
They revealed a lot and understood each other more]

1050
01:09:21,640 --> 01:09:24,080
[Cho Yun Jae: It's so frustrating.]

1051
01:09:24,080 --> 01:09:27,850
[Cho Yun Jae: He'll probably still
call Sun Wook anyway.]

1052
01:09:27,850 --> 01:09:30,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Whatever choice you make,
I will respect it.]

1053
01:09:30,290 --> 01:09:32,859
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Today's date
was good too.]

1054
01:09:32,859 --> 01:09:35,359
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But I can't help it.
The pressure is still high.]

1055
01:09:35,529 --> 01:09:38,090
[Lee Hyun Jun: I have to
make things clear anyway.]

1056
01:09:38,090 --> 01:09:41,670
[Cho Yun Jae: I wish time could turn back.]

1057
01:09:42,130 --> 01:09:44,899
[Chaos descends upon the Men's House]

1058
01:09:44,899 --> 01:09:47,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm really torn.
I don't know who to call.]

1059
01:09:47,740 --> 01:09:50,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't actually
think about it for long.]

1060
01:09:50,240 --> 01:09:53,340
[Kim Han Gyeol: I just want
to go on a date with you.]

1061
01:09:53,340 --> 01:09:55,950
[Oh Min Seong: Being able to date every day
makes me so happy.]

1062
01:09:56,210 --> 01:09:57,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: See you later.]

1063
01:09:57,780 --> 01:10:00,720
[Lee Hyun Jun: Thank you for telling me
your true feelings.]

1064
01:10:00,720 --> 01:10:03,250
[Kim Sun Wook: Once you say it,
you have to stand by it.]

1065
01:10:03,350 --> 01:10:06,360
[Cho Yun Jae: I feel like I'm just
short on luck.]

1066
01:10:06,360 --> 01:10:09,330
[Cho Yun Jae: It feels so unfair.]

1067
01:10:09,990 --> 01:10:11,540
[When will these chaotic feelings
find peace?]
